{"tid":38882,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"佢話我唔愛佢   要同我分手⋯⋯","createTime":"2016-12-14T08:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T08:43:14.000Z","uid":23197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2dd2d291ed38476833d09b68f68910d8d4346b1","tid":38882,"uid":23197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:14:58.000Z","msg":"果日放假同佢岀去行街 <br />\n本身都好地地 都係行下街 食下飯<br />\n中途佢話見到隻杯好靚想買 但我唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁佢已經開始有啲怨言.....我諗住過左陣佢就會冇事所以冇理佢<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就返我屋企訓 都係攬攬錫錫果啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n突然間佢摸一摸我條巨龍之後喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我心諗咩事<br />\n原來佢話我唔夠硬...話我唔愛佢 要同我分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我一時火遮眼就應承左 跟住佢即刻著返晒啲衫褲岀去買果個杯...仲話以後都唔再需要我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點算....而家好後悔講左分手....."},{"pid":"f98a3fde58cc6a28c24a76d40c79478d22976064","tid":38882,"uid":18418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:25:07.000Z","msg":"為左隻杯分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be00a3dcb658abb93944b9b6414277a6d930089","tid":38882,"uid":7567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"飛機杯"},{"pid":"e75443daf733933fc810d0dddbcc2766e6cf2cbc","tid":38882,"uid":38431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:27:01.000Z","msg":"隻杯比你硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ed82308fe664179e4b1568db6aafa5cec8889a","tid":38882,"uid":23197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:43:14.000Z","msg":"好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}